00:40:01,031 --> 00:40:04,568
It wasn't?
I thought we stunk.

576
00:40:04,603 --> 00:40:06,569
Well...

577
00:40:06,604 --> 00:40:08,571
<i>I wouldn't
put it that way.</i>

