that I said that, okay?</i>

591
00:41:04,995 --> 00:41:06,962
- Okay.
- Let's do it again.

592
00:41:06,997 --> 00:41:09,765
<i>Right this time.
Stand up straight.</i>

593
00:41:09,800 --> 00:41:12,803
