00:41:12,838 --> 00:41:14,772
<i>Stop sign. Beautiful.
Let's go.</i>

595
00:41:14,807 --> 00:41:17,870
Five, six, seven, and...

596
00:41:17,905 --> 00:41:20,934
Tempo, tempo, tempo!

597
00:41:23,814 --> 00:41:26,250
<i>Don't open the presents,
all right, on the airplane.</i>

598
00:41:26,285 --> 00:41:29,698
It's time to board.
Time to go.

